		                                                                <td
		                                                                    style="width:223.1pt; border-style:solid; border-width:0.75pt; padding-right:5.03pt; padding-left:5.03pt; vertical-align:top; -aw-border:0.5pt single">
		                                                                    <p style="margin-bottom:3pt; font-size:9pt">
		                                                                        <span>3a. 1 WBDC in Kohat constructed and 1
		                                                                            technical training institute for girls in
		                                                                            Peshawar upgraded (2020 baseline: 0) (OP
		                                                                            2.4.1)</span></p>
		                                                                </td>
