		                                                                    <p style="margin-bottom:3pt; font-size:9pt">
		                                                                        <span>3c. At least 100 women entrepreneurs
		                                                                            have established green enterprises with
		                                                                            the material and business under the
		                                                                            Community Incentive Fund established by
		                                                                            the project (2020 baseline: 0) (OP
		                                                                            2.4.1)</span></p>
