		                                                                    <p style="margin-bottom:3pt; font-size:9pt">
		                                                                        <span>3d. At least 55 female beneficiaries of
		                                                                            the projectâ€™s scholarship program earned
		                                                                            university degrees in fields related to
		                                                                            urban water supply and sanitation (2020
		                                                                            baseline: 0) (OP 2.2.1)</span></p>
		                                                                </td>
